      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused machine featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The naturally aspirated powerplant is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for superlative handling. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain synchronization are excellent, making this a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
